Alikhan Tursunbekov!

Timer and Stopwatch iOS App

Overview

This iOS app provides users with both a timer and stopwatch functionality, allowing them to easily measure time intervals for various tasks and activities. Whether you need to time a workout, track cooking durations, or manage your study sessions, this app has you covered.

Features

Timer: Set a specific countdown duration and get notified when the timer reaches zero.
Stopwatch: Start, pause, resume, and reset the stopwatch to measure elapsed time accurately.
User-Friendly Interface: Intuitive design for effortless navigation and usage.
Customizable Alerts: Choose from a variety of alert sounds and vibrations to notify you when the timer or stopwatch ends.
